<div class="_j_content_box">
	        <div data-seq="272742955" data-index="1" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">前 言</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278250377">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;好久没长途旅行了，自从7年前去了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12684.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="台湾" target="_blank">台湾</a>和<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/23934.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="江南" target="_blank">江南</a>水乡，这几年都没出过省，就在2017年，我有机会去了一趟<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>，虽然距离<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>9天亲子之旅已经过去有1个半月了，很多记忆也都开始模糊，但是一看到手机里、电脑里存的那将近800张照片，我忍不住要把这段经历记录下来，因为这是一次难忘之旅，可以说是毕生难忘的！<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;其实<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>是我一直想去的地方，这次是趁着我父母带着我儿子去我哥我大嫂<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>的家小住一段时间，我也正好有一些假期，所以就跟着去了，我哥他们的家地方不大，我父母和我儿子就住他们家，我住附近的宾馆，还好，隔得不远，走几分钟就到。<br />

        </p>
            <div data-seq="278251293" data-index="2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">DAY 1</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278251813">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我是在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10088.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="广州" target="_blank">广州</a>南站坐上午10点的动车去的，这是我第二次在在南站坐车，也是第一次一个人坐动车去那么远的地方。列车飞驰，一路上的风景不停地变换着，虽然都差不多，天气也不是很好，但一想到8个小时之后就见到父母和儿子，还有很久都没见的大哥大嫂他们，心里就充满期待和激动！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278251981" data-seq="278251982" data-pid="278251981" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="854285">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8161006/278251981.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:951px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/67/75/wKgBEFpI-SiAAU7xAAVwgnNQob814.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/67/75/wKgBEFpI-SiAAU7xAAVwgnNQob814.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278251981" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/854285.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="854285" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="traffic"></i>北京西站
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278252190">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;经过8小时的车程，终于在晚上6点左右到达<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>西站了，一出站就感受到寒气逼人！在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10088.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="广州" target="_blank">广州</a>还可以穿一两件衣服，但在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>，我马上把厚衣服穿上，这里比<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10088.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="广州" target="_blank">广州</a>冻多了！车站和广场上的人都穿着厚厚的衣服。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278252688" data-seq="278252693" data-pid="278252688" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="854285">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8161006/278252688.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/67/C5/wKgBEFpI-XyAOkncAAZHC9zB8u020.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/67/C5/wKgBEFpI-XyAOkncAAZHC9zB8u020.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278252688" alt="" />
