                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278252690" data-seq="278252694" data-pid="278252690" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="854285">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8161006/278252690.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/67/C5/wKgBEFpI-XyADZecAAYLFG8pmVU69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/67/C5/wKgBEFpI-XyADZecAAYLFG8pmVU69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278252690" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/854285.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="854285" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="traffic"></i>北京西站
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278252692" data-seq="278252695" data-pid="278252692" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="854285">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8161006/278252692.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/67/C6/wKgBEFpI-X2AUuccAAemCZHh6Mc83.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/67/C6/wKgBEFpI-X2AUuccAAemCZHh6Mc83.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278252692" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/854285.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="854285" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="traffic"></i>北京西站
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278253055">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我和我哥在广场碰面之后，我哥就打了滴滴，半个小时就他家了，见到我儿子当然很开心啦，一家人吃过晚饭后，商讨了一下第二天的行程，我哥便带着到酒店住下了。<br />

        </p>
            <div data-seq="278253140" data-index="3" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">DAY 2</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278253360">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;一大早，我就到了我哥家，吃过早餐之后，我和我爸还有我儿子便开始<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>之旅第一天的行程，第一站是去地坛公园。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;地坛公园又称方泽坛，是古都<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>五坛中的第二大坛。地坛公园位于<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>市东城区定门外大街，占地37.4公顷。公园始建于明代嘉靖九年(公元1530年)，是明清两朝帝王祭祀&quot;皇地袛神&quot;的场所，也是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>现存的最大的祭地之坛。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;从我哥家要坐大概1个小时的公交车去地坛公园，我第一次坐<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>的公交车，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>的公交车原来上下车都要打卡的，这和<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10088.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="广州" target="_blank">广州</a>很不同，开始很不习惯，但慢慢也习惯了，不用爸爸提醒也记得打卡，连我儿子也记得，常常嚷着要打卡，呵呵……<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;一个小时后，我们便来到地坛公园，首先引入眼帘的是高大气派的牌坊，牌坊上刻有精美的花纹和雕刻，可惜那天阴沉沉的，不然在蓝天白云的映衬下会更加漂亮！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278254173" data-seq="278254177" data-pid="278254173" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3526">
