                    <i class="house"></i>地坛公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278254749">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;牌坊后便是一条长廊，长廊的两边是金灿灿的银杏树，地上也洒满银杏树叶，一眼望去，满眼都是黄色，人们尽情地拍照，甚至挥洒着地上的银杏树叶。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278255075" data-seq="278255080" data-pid="278255075" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3526">
