            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278256001">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我爸还带着我儿子，两爷孙一起找一片好看的银杏树叶，这个场景不禁勾起我对小时候的回忆，或许也有这样的场景吧&nbsp;。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278256059" data-seq="278256060" data-pid="278256059" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3526">
