            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278256416">
            不一会就找到了一片，我儿子还举起来给我看呢<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278256460" data-seq="278256461" data-pid="278256460" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3526">
