        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3526.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3526" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>地坛公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278258365" data-seq="278258370" data-pid="278258365" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3526">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8161006/278258365.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/6A/8A/wKgBEFpI_EiAIDf4AA-s22oIRhI68.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/6A/8A/wKgBEFpI_EiAIDf4AA-s22oIRhI68.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278258365" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3526.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3526" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>地坛公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278258665">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;游览了一个小时后，我们离开地坛公园、去下一个经典——孔庙和国子监。孔庙位于<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>东城区国子监街，为<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>元、明、清三朝祭祀孔子的场所。1302年(元大德六年)建，大德十年建成。孔庙，门内院落共有三进，中轴线上的建筑从南向北依次为大成门、大成殿、崇圣门及崇圣祠。有元、明、清三代的进士题名碑198块，为研究<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>古代科举制度的重要文献资料。孔庙旁边就是国子监，国子监是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>古代隋朝以后的中央官学，为<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>古代教育体系中的最高学府，又称国子学或国子寺。<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278259603" data-seq="278259615" data-pid="278259603" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3517">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8161006/278259603.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/6A/F5/wKgBEFpI_LmAeZ2cAAzwlILI_bk50.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/6A/F5/wKgBEFpI_LmAeZ2cAAzwlILI_bk50.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278259603" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3517.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3517" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>孔庙和国子监
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278259604" data-seq="278259616" data-pid="278259604" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3517">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8161006/278259604.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/6A/F8/wKgBEFpI_LuAB0rAABY3R17SAd856.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/6A/F8/wKgBEFpI_LuAB0rAABY3R17SAd856.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278259604" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3517.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3517" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>孔庙和国子监
